OL,3,CVaughan Gething set to become first
OL,4,Cminister of Wales today
OL,6,FSenedd members are expected to confirm
OL,7,Flater today that Vaughan Gething will
OL,8,Fbecome the next first minister of
OL,9,FWales.
OL,11,FHe is set to take over from Mark
OL,12,FDrakeford who resigned from the top
OL,13,Fjob on Tuesday.
OL,15,FBut opposition parties will vote
OL,16,Fagainst Mr Gething's appointment and
OL,17,Fnominate their own leaders instead.
