OL,3,CVaughan Gething set to become first
OL,4,Cminister of Wales today
OL,6,FThe new first minister is due to be
OL,7,Fselected on Wednesday by the Senedd
OL,8,Ffollowing the Labour leadership
OL,9,Fannouncement on Saturday.
OL,11,FMr Gething was elected as the new
OL,12,Fleader of Welsh Labour on Saturday, 16
OL,13,FMarch. He received 51.7% of the vote,
OL,14,Fwhile his rival Jeremy Miles secured
OL,15,F48.3%.
OL,17,FAs a result, Mr Drakeford, who has
OL,18,Fbeen the party leader since December
OL,19,F2018, has stepped down as first
OL,20,Fminister this week.
