OL,3,CVaughan Gething set to become first
OL,4,Cminister of Wales today
OL,6,FHe delivered his resignation speech on
OL,7,FTuesday following his final FMQs.
OL,9,FIn his final address as first
OL,10,Fminister, Mr Drakeford said he was
OL,11,F"most grateful of all to the people"
OL,12,Fthat he has been "lucky enough to
OL,13,Fserve".
OL,15,FTo become first minister, a candidate
OL,16,Fmust be nominated by Members of the
OL,17,FSenedd (MSs) and voted upon in the
OL,18,FWelsh Parliament.
