OL,3,CVaughan Gething set to become first
OL,4,Cminister of Wales today
OL,6,FOnce the current first minister
OL,7,Fresigns, the Senedd has 28 days to
OL,8,Fnominate a successor.
OL,10,FAlthough any MS can run for first
OL,11,Fminister, typically the leader of the
OL,12,Fparty with the most MSs assumes the
OL,13,Frole.
OL,15,FIn this case, new Welsh Labour leader
OL,16,FMr Gething is almost certainly set to
OL,17,Fbecome Wales' first minister.
OL,19,FIf there are multiple candidates, MSs
OL,20,Fvote in a single round and the winner
OL,21,Fis determined by a simple majority.
