OL,3,CVaughan Gething set to become first
OL,4,Cminister of Wales today
OL,6,FMr Gething has already made history,
OL,7,Fbecoming the first black person to be
OL,8,Felected Welsh Labour leader. Should he
OL,9,Fbe appointed first minister on
OL,10,FWednesday, he would be the first black
OL,11,Fleader of any European country.
