OL,3,CVaughan Gething set to become first
OL,4,Cminister of Wales today
OL,6,FMr Gething's appointment as leader of
OL,7,FWelsh Labour has not come without its
OL,8,Fchallenges. He has already faced
OL,9,Fintense scrutiny over his role as
OL,10,Fhealth minister during the Covid-19
OL,11,Fpandemic at the UK Covid Inquiry,
OL,12,Fwhile his leadership campaign was
OL,13,Fovershadowed by his controversial
OL,14,Facceptance of a #200,000 donation from
OL,15,Fa company whose director was convicted
OL,16,Fof environmental offences.
OL,18,FOnce the Senedd selects a nominee, the
OL,19,Fpresiding officer sends a letter to
OL,20,Fthe King recommending that person for
OL,21,Fappointment.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/9
