OL,3,CVaughan Gething set to become first
OL,4,Cminister of Wales today
OL,6,FAfter approval from the King, the new
OL,7,Ffirst minister will be sworn in via
OL,8,FRoyal Warrant. They will take the
OL,9,Fofficial oath before a judge and
OL,10,Fpledge to serve King Charles III.
OL,12,FTypically, the new first minister
OL,13,Fbecomes a member of the Privy Council
OL,14,Fand may have a private audience with
OL,15,Fthe King.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/9
