OL,3,CVaughan Gething set to become first
OL,4,Cminister of Wales today
OL,6,FSpeaking ahead of the vote, Andrew RT
OL,7,FDavies - leader of the Welsh
OL,8,FConservatives in the Senedd - said of
OL,9,FMr Gething: "He's gotten off to a
OL,10,Fdifficult start with the donation of
OL,11,F#200,000 and the disquiet on his own
OL,12,Fbackbenchers.
OL,14,F"It's not a great way to start your
OL,15,Ftenure as first minister.
OL,17,F"My name will be going forward to be
OL,18,Fconsidered for first minister in the
OL,19,Fvote, but Labour do have the votes so
OL,20,Fwe can take it that Vaughan will be
OL,21,Fthat individual.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/9
