OL,6,F"But he's got a lot of fires to put
OL,7,Fout on his own backbenches and within
OL,8,Fhis party before he can get his head
OL,9,Faround the really important job of
OL,10,Fbeing first minister and delivering
OL,11,Ffor the people of Wales."
